                        <seg type="script">Crude, irregular.</seg>
                        <seg type="ink">Black, vivid red.</seg>
                        <date>Mid-18th century - mid-19th century.</date>
                        <list type="abbreviations">
                           <item>ይካ፡ for ይበል፡ ካህን፡</item>
                           <item>ይዲ፡ for ይበል፡ ዲያቆን፡</item>
                        </list>
                        <seg type="rubrication">Nomina sacra; incipit of Text I; directives to the
                           ministers and their abbreviations; titles of the books to be read;
                           elements of the punctuation signs; elements of Ethiopic numerals. &#xD;
                           On the incipit page of Text I (fol. 1r), two lines are rubricated
                           (alternating with a black line).</seg>
